  <text>
    <body>
      <div type="transcription" xml:id="transcription_aad_0060" xml:lang="de">
        <div type="corresp">
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00241/" ed="1r" type="sheet"/>
          <div type="letter_message" hand="#hand_blue_auden">
            <opener>
              <dateline>
                <placeName>
                  <address xml:lang="en">
                    <lb/><rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_29">77 St Mark's Place
                    <lb/>New York City
                    <lb/>New York 1003</rs>
                  </address>
                </placeName>
                <del rend="overstrike" hand="#hand_blue_auden">
                  <unclear>
                    <date>
                      <lb/>Mar
                    </date>
                  </unclear>
                </del>
                <date>
                  <lb/>Mar<subst><del rend="overwritten" hand="#hand_blue_auden"><unclear>c</unclear></del><add place="superimposed" hand="#hand_blue_auden">z</add></subst> 15<hi rend="superscript">ten</hi>. 1969
                </date>
              </dateline>
              <salute>
                <lb/>Lieber <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_107">Hugo</rs>:
              </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>
              <lb/>Besten Da<unclear>m</unclear>k für deinen Brief. Es tut
              <lb/>mir leid dass der Tank-stelle Plan zu grunde
              <lb/>gefallen ist. Es ist nicht nötig d<gap reason="illegible" unit="char" atLeast="1" atMost="2"/> Scheck
              <lb/>zurück zu schicken : zerre<gap reason="illegible" unit="char" atLeast="1" atMost="2"/> sich an .
            </p>
            <p>
              <lb/>Am ersten April reise <unclear><subst><del rend="overwritten" hand="#hand_blue_auden">s</del><add place="superimposed" hand="#hand_blue_auden">i</add></subst></unclear>ch zu erst nach
              <lb/><rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_13">Athene</rs> und dann nach <rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_359">Jerusalem</rs>. <unclear>I</unclear>ch weiss noch
              <lb/>nicht genau wann <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_4">Chester</rs> und ich nach <rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_10"><foreign xml:lang="en">Austria</foreign></rs>
              <lb/>reise<unclear>m</unclear>&#x2013;glaube ungefähr 10<hi rend="superscript">ten</hi>.&#x2013; aber natürlich
              <lb/>lasse ich dich wissen vorher.
            </p>
            <closer>
              <salute>
                <lb/>Al<unclear>l</unclear>er gutes
              </salute>
              <salute>
                <lb/>Dein Freund
              </salute>
              <signed>
                <lb/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_1">Wystan</rs> .
              </signed>
            </closer>
          </div>
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00242/" ed="1v" type="sheet"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </body>
